# WHV Australia — Vercel Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add these in: Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Frontend (prefix VITE_ so Vite exposes them to the browser) ──────────────

# Stripe publishable key — safe to expose
VITE_STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_live_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# HMAC secret for cancel verification — must match CANCEL_HMAC_SECRET below
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
VITE_CANCEL_HMAC_SECRET=your_secret_here


# ── Backend (server-only, never sent to browser) ─────────────────────────────

# Stripe secret key — NEVER expose this
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Stripe webhook signing secret
# Get from: Stripe Dashboard → Developers → Webhooks → your endpoint → Signing secret
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# HMAC secret for cancel verification — must match VITE_CANCEL_HMAC_SECRET above
CANCEL_HMAC_SECRET=your_secret_here

# Resend API key for transactional emails (free tier: 3,000/month)
# Sign up at: https://resend.com
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SETUP CHECKLIST
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. STRIPE KEYS
#    Stripe Dashboard → Developers → API Keys
#    → Copy Publishable key  → VITE_STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY
#    → Copy Secret key       → STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
#
# 2. STRIPE WEBHOOK
#    Stripe Dashboard → Developers → Webhooks → Add endpoint
#    → URL: https://your-domain.vercel.app/api/stripe-webhook
#    → Events: invoice.payment_succeeded, invoice.payment_failed,
#              customer.subscription.updated, customer.subscription.deleted
#    → Copy signing secret   → STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
#
# 3. CANCEL HMAC SECRET
#    Run: openssl rand -hex 32
#    Set same value for BOTH CANCEL_HMAC_SECRET and VITE_CANCEL_HMAC_SECRET
#
# 4. RESEND (email sending)
#    Sign up free at resend.com
#    Add and verify your domain (whvguides.com.au)
#    Create API key → RESEND_API_KEY
#
# 5. Add all variables in Vercel Dashboard
#    Project → Settings → Environment Variables → Add each one
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
